Looking at the data, I can see this is a balance sheet with various accounts. The task asks me to identify expense items specifically.

From the balance sheet:

- Accumulated Depreciation had an end value of 91505.05 on 2024-02-05

This accumulated depreciation represents an expense that has been recognized in the profit and loss statement.
